{"tid":774324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【袁容聯婚】恩恩豬(容海恩)今日結婚  半島擺4圍","createTime":"2018-08-10T08:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T08:37:15.000Z","uid":103156,"like":9,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"1550f2fa8cf47b4e347e329bf966fff95ff2d5dd","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"【李八方online】恩恩豬結婚半島擺4圍 雙喜臨門？容媽咁樣答<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58545895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58545895&d=wx6iEg62ONdXxhH%2BTr%2BZ2JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9f4f036f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58545895&h=aba87321\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58545895</a><br />\n<br />\n萬眾期待，41歲嘅新民黨議員容海恩（恩恩豬）今日同政策總裁袁彌昌拉埋天窗喇！兩人喺證婚議式前一同見記者，見恩恩豬疑似粗身大細，都仲著住4吋斗零高踭鞋，仲要落樓梯，八方都替佢捏一把冷汗，好在袁總好快就出手護花，拖住老婆。<br />\n<br />\n恩恩豬一身白紗，笑容滿面咁，八方都真係戥佢開心呀！<span style=\"color: red;\">袁彌昌對於老婆似乎好滿意，舉起手指公話：「right choice ，係最好嘅選擇」而於恩恩豬就希望老公「一路都係咁好」喎</span>！<br />\n<br />\n問到有咩心情，恩恩豬就話原來結婚真係好多嘢搞，坦言「要結婚完來都唔易呀」，有好多嘢要籌備，袁彌昌就話老婆係「right choice ，係最好嘅選擇」。咁係唔係就快做爸爸呢？袁總就話「有消息會話畀大家知，都有咁嘅希望喎」。"},{"pid":"dace20540dd89e73c7a92bf9592dd6ab9e75d87c","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":8,"dislike":77,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=94853f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=89675664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82397167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=69b5b859&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6a93b8cefbbcbf10ebf66ede4fc90343f464c11","tid":774324,"uid":156652,"like":226,"dislike":3,"score":223,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"四圍？不如落M記食"},{"pid":"2c3696152e90fb94ca0e683ee85c228b670b9da6","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"葉太話祝佢哋兩個早生貴子，仲話送咗銀行禮卷畀佢哋，等佢哋鍾意買咩就買咩：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164440_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164440_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=409f4cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被問到恩恩豬係唔係雙喜臨門呢？Alice(右)話今日只係講結婚，容媽媽(左)好識做，淨係話佢唔知咋：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/164514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F164514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=597c69a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf6ef0b3008a427de85e2a071b3b9f048409e0be","tid":774324,"uid":85629,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"死死聲 唔好聽<br />\n但容小姐唔介意 證明佢唔係信奉中國文化習俗既人<br />\n破舊立新"},{"pid":"bcaf037888ddcb2a94630fa4b4802b2a69f5e0cd","tid":774324,"uid":2545,"like":148,"dislike":1,"score":147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"竟然得4圍<br />\n是咪證明新民黨冇朋友"},{"pid":"06d9171b262343d781374bfdf3e875e7442dcd75","tid":774324,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baf17aa703247847b26ddc260aa1e263439840a0","tid":774324,"uid":31208,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"袁彌明有冇去？"},{"pid":"10616370bf4ac480f6a00faa628a89701eb5470c","tid":774324,"uid":52881,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"做得議員人面咁廣加埋紅底先得四圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8df98c234c272fe30d7b07185ae7227e8b0da4","tid":774324,"uid":6293,"like":93,"dislike":2,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"趕到咁，你話唔係有左都冇人信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6984bcb388666f0230f290728f4964f9a4456386","tid":774324,"uid":189048,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2021ed8cdae1405f693fa5e72579361574fab315","tid":774324,"uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"10616370bf4ac480f6a00faa628a89701eb5470c","tid":774324,"uid":52881,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"做得議員人面咁廣加埋紅底先得四圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"半島咁貴，四圍差唔多啦"},{"pid":"15a5d2af9f79e7e249904dce10bf6cd92b54c049","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"至於姐妹之一嘅工聯會議員麥美娟就透露，今朝都有按傳統玩新郎，遊戲就包括邊做掌上壓邊食生果，同埋互餵環節，仲強調「好衛生架」，但佢就無講開門利是有幾多喇。而袁彌昌個妹<span style=\"color: red;\">袁彌明就同丈夫林雨陽現身，不過就避開無見記者。</span><br />\n<br />\n恩恩豬同袁彌昌下晝喺半島酒店7樓宴請親朋好友。半島今日就貼出告示講到明「Eunice &amp; Derek Wedding ceremony」今日舉行。<span style=\"color: red;\">據聞儀式下晝1點舉行，1點半係午宴。</span><br />\n<br />\n早喺中午12點左右，麥美娟就帶埋恩恩豬嘅媽媽現身見記者，容媽媽一身紅旗袍加上一大串珍珠頸鏈，睇落非常雍容華貴，<span style=\"color: red;\">問到佢對於女婿滿唔滿意，容媽媽笑晒咁話「101分呀！好滿意」</span>，佢仲向在場記者派餅卡同利是，好喜氣洋洋。<br />\n<br />\n容媽媽又透露，今早已經喺酒店完成斟茶等儀式。<span style=\"color: red;\">恩恩豬係唔係雙喜臨門呢？Alice就即時擋駕，話「今日只係講結婚」，容媽媽就好識做，淨係話佢唔知咋。</span><br />\n<br />\n臨近1點，賓客都陸續到場，恩恩豬同袁總嘅「媒人」新民黨主席葉劉淑儀就一襲白裙現身，外套上仲有Lace，衣著上畀足面。<span style=\"color: red;\">葉太話祝佢哋兩個早生貴子</span>，仲話送咗銀行禮卷畀佢哋，等佢哋鍾意買咩就買咩。而新民黨副主席潘國山亦有現身，不過就十問九唔應。"},{"pid":"ffcf85bdcd7a789227a57ecc086a825818c6489e","tid":774324,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"4圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683d1e5242792294642878df2abcd42e792adc7d","tid":774324,"uid":49197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"4圍...不如旅遊結婚算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719cc2db01ec28cc186fd9a2711fe56516b471ce","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"baf17aa703247847b26ddc260aa1e263439840a0","tid":774324,"uid":31208,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"袁彌明有冇去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"「而袁彌昌個妹袁彌明就同丈夫林雨陽現身，不過就避開無見記者。」"},{"pid":"0e867e62076a93c85a3f3f83450b6aa3438aa3eb","tid":774324,"uid":44562,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"真係要四圍走 ?"},{"pid":"bbce976011224d35083618edb017e864fc34944d","tid":774324,"uid":18587,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"無得放婚假同產假呀！會俾廿蚊張屌！"},{"pid":"bcf1ccf82b2f5a1f5d06782d36cf2ddc7e8518c8","tid":774324,"uid":19552,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"683d1e5242792294642878df2abcd42e792adc7d","tid":774324,"uid":49197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"4圍...不如旅遊結婚算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"可能咁能樣一圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn3.esdcdn.com/wow/attachment/201507/23/84572_1437661457Te7q.jpg?w=480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn3.esdcdn.com%2Fwow%2Fattachment%2F201507%2F23%2F84572_1437661457Te7q.jpg%3Fw%3D480&h=45e6e9c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1b04bb13cbc09e658ca7a2775a1fe8936ac65e7","tid":774324,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"TOTAL要幾錢呢"},{"pid":"7ec6b5ded3307df8616ba5583167ba4ee2478c75","tid":774324,"uid":90820,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「要結婚<span style=\"color: red;\">完</span>來都唔易呀」</blockquote><br />\n原來文盲都可以是但寫啲垃圾登報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9008c50526505804a397e1ad2488e59df8fc953","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/165847_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F165847_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0d70edba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多情自古空餘恨，此恨綿綿無絕期。"},{"pid":"9d712cebcd427afaed416cd4defbe85f9e28f4ec","tid":774324,"uid":33864,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d9008c50526505804a397e1ad2488e59df8fc953","tid":774324,"uid":103156,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/165847_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa